text: WVTT may refer to: *WVTT-CD, on TV channel 34 (virtual 25) and licensed to Olean, New York *WCGH, a radio station (103.9 FM) licensed to serve Eldred, Pennsylvania, United States, which held the call sign WVTT in 2011 and again in 2019 *WAGL (FM), on 96.7 and licensed to Portville, New York, was WVTT from 2011 to 2019
title: WVTT
